snippet: Ai Miyazato of Japan shot an eight-under-par 64 for a one-shot lead in the season-ending Titleholders in Naples, Florida.
abstract: Ai Miyazato takes second-round lead at Titleholders golf tournament in Naples, Fla; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Ai Miyazato of Japan shot an eight-under-par 64 for a one-shot lead in the season-ending Titleholders in Naples, Florida.

headline.seo: Miyazato Holds Slim Lead in Florida
